Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:25.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(序幕)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:37.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(极北之地 1857年)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:00:55.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船长\N{\rEN\blur3}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:02.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船长\N{\rEN\blur3}Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:05.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能聊聊吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.08,0:01:14.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们必须破冰前行\N{\rEN\blur3}We must break through the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都很饿 也累坏了\N{\rEN\blur3}The men are hungry and exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.08,0:01:20.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是继续这样下去 恐怕会付出代价\N{\rEN\blur3}We cannot keep up this pace without consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.29,0:01:26.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家听着\N{\rEN\blur3}Listen up, men!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:32.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们拖得越久 冰就冻得越牢固\N{\rEN\blur3}The more we delay the labor, the firmer the grasp of the ice will become.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:34.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}继续干活\N{\rEN\blur3}The work continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:36.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}各组轮流作业\N{\rEN\blur3}Rotate each group.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.71,0:01:37.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 请听我说\N{\rEN\blur3}Sir, with respect...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.46,0:01:39.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家需要一句准话\N{\rEN\blur3}The men need assurances.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:40.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准话\N{\rEN\blur3}Assurances?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:44.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对 就是让船动起来之后 我们会回圣彼得堡去\N{\rEN\blur3}Yes, that we will head back to St. Petersburg once we free the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们觉得我们的船航行不了多久了 他们想知道...\N{\rEN\blur3}They don't think we'll be seaworthy for long and they want to know--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:49.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都听好了\N{\rEN\blur3}Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:55.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别的任何事情 都不是你们和这位长官该考虑的\N{\rEN\blur3}It is neither your place, nor the officer here, to think anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:59.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们接受了一项任务 就要把它完成\N{\rEN\blur3}We signed up for a mission and we will see it to completion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:01.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一定会到达北极\N{\rEN\blur3}We will reach the North Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都听明白了吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Is it understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船长 那里爆炸了...\N{\rEN\blur3}An explosion, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离这里大约三公里\N{\rEN\blur3}About two miles away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:53.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去救人\N{\rEN\blur3}Get the men.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雪橇犬没受伤\N{\rEN\blur3}The sled dogs are unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.12,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那这血是哪来的\N{\rEN\blur3}Then where does all this blood come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:16.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}船长 在那里\N{\rEN\blur3}Over here, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:20.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有个受了伤的人 他流了好多血\N{\rEN\blur3}A wounded man, he's lost a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肩膀受伤了 腿断了\N{\rEN\blur3}Wound to the shoulder, his leg is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是被熊咬的吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Bear attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:29.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得不是 船长\N{\rEN\blur3}I don't think so, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉森 来帮我把这只靴子脱下来\N{\rEN\blur3}Larsen, help me with his boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:43.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是个假肢\N{\rEN\blur3}A prosthetic leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把他抬船上去\N{\rEN\blur3}Put him on the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:57.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快 抬上船 赶紧\N{\rEN\blur3}Hurry! To the ship! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拉森 那东西来了\N{\rEN\blur3}Larsen, that thing is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:09.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}步枪准备\N{\rEN\blur3}Ready the rifles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听我指令\N{\rEN\blur3}On my command.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:21.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瞄准\N{\rEN\blur3}Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:24.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开火\N{\rEN\blur3}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:36.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一组\N{\rEN\blur3}Next group!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:41.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开火\N{\rEN\blur3}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:56.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全部上船\N{\rEN\blur3}All to the ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们抬上船的那个人呢\N{\rEN\blur3}Where is that man we brought onboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:19.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他在哪里\N{\rEN\blur3}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那究竟是什么东西 它想干什么\N{\rEN\blur3}What is that thing? What does it want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.13,0:05:34.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把他给我\N{\rEN\blur3}Bring him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喇叭枪 拉森 拿喇叭枪\N{\rEN\blur3}The blunderbuss. Larsen, get the blunderbuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:06.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:20.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我杀了它\N{\rEN\blur3}I killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.42,0:06:22.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我杀了它\N{\rEN\blur3}I killed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:37.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它还活着\N{\rEN\blur3}It's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}梯子\N{\rEN\blur3}Ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快收梯子\N{\rEN\blur3}Pull up the ladder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.17,0:06:58.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把他交出来\N{\rEN\blur3}Bring him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还剩几发\N{\rEN\blur3}How many shots are left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:20.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一发 但杀不了它\N{\rEN\blur3}One, but it can't kill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:21.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道\N{\rEN\blur3}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不是要打他\N{\rEN\blur3}I'm not aiming for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.54,0:08:18.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是鸦片酊 能止痛 喝吧\N{\rEN\blur3}Laudanum, to ease the pain. Drink it. Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:25.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我这是在哪里\N{\rEN\blur3}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是丹麦皇家航船霍莱松特号\N{\rEN\blur3}You are on the Royal Danish ship, Horisont.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:29.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是安德森船长 这位是邬德森医生\N{\rEN\blur3}I'm Captain Anderson. This is Dr. Udsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:31.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怪物杀了你们多少人\N{\rEN\blur3}How many of your men did it kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:34.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}六个\N{\rEN\blur3}Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:37.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它会回来 让更多人丧命\N{\rEN\blur3}It will come back and kill many more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:41.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不把我交出去 你们都会没命\N{\rEN\blur3}All of you, if necessary, unless you deliver me to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:43.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会的 它不在了\N{\rEN\blur3}No, no. It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它沉入了冰水 死了\N{\rEN\blur3}It sank in the freezing waters. It's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它没死\N{\rEN\blur3}No, it is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:48.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它死不了\N{\rEN\blur3}It cannot die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直尝试彻底摧毁它\N{\rEN\blur3}I have tried to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:55.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管你们信不信\N{\rEN\blur3}Whether you believe me or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:09:00.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它都会回来 找我\N{\rEN\blur3}it will come back... for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等它真的回来了\N{\rEN\blur3}And when it does,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定要把我送到外面的冰面上\N{\rEN\blur3}you must promise that you will put me out on the ice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:07.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让它带走我\N{\rEN\blur3}and let it take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}求你们了\N{\rEN\blur3}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那究竟是什么\N{\rEN\blur3}What manner of creature is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:16.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什么样的魔鬼造出来的\N{\rEN\blur3}What manner of devil made him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我\N{\rEN\blur3}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:22.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是我\N{\rEN\blur3}I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我亲手造的他\N{\rEN\blur3}I made him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:32.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我本已下定决心 让那些罪恶的记忆和我一同消亡\N{\rEN\blur3}I had determined that the memory of my evils should die with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准备好了\N{\rEN\blur3}It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:37.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来我要说的话 有些是真的\N{\rEN\blur3}Some of what I will tell you is fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:42.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有些是假的 但这是真的\N{\rEN\blur3}Some is not, but it is all true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:44.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}My name is Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多·弗兰肯斯坦\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor Frankenstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的名字是父亲起的\N{\rEN\blur3}It was my father who gave me that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道这名字是什么意思吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Do you know what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该是征服者的意思\N{\rEN\blur3}I believe I do, yes. Conqueror.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.58,0:09:57.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赢得一切的人\N{\rEN\blur3}One that wins it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:59.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 一切因他而起\N{\rEN\blur3}Yes. It all started with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的父亲\N{\rEN\blur3}My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有我的母亲\N{\rEN\blur3}And my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.58,0:10:10.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(第一部分 维克多的故事)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:13.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:17.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:23.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快下来 你父亲来了\N{\rEN\blur3}Come down, your father is arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈 妈妈\N{\rEN\blur3}Maman? Maman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲 我在这里\N{\rEN\blur3}I'm here, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:35.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里\N{\rEN\blur3}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:41.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我父亲是男爵 也是个杰出的外科医生\N{\rEN\blur3}My father was a baron and a preeminent surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:44.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他娶我母亲 很大程度上为了利益\N{\rEN\blur3}He had married my mother largely out of convenience,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:47.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为母亲的陪嫁相当丰厚 而且她是贵族出身\N{\rEN\blur3}as her dowry was considerable and her lineage noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:53.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她带来的资金 足以让父亲维持爵位和家族产业\N{\rEN\blur3}It furnished my father with the means to preserve his rank and family estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:08.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}日常生活中 从来看不见父亲的身影\N{\rEN\blur3}He was absent from our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:11.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而每当他回到家 所有人都对他唯命是从\N{\rEN\blur3}but when he came home, the entire household bent to his will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:12.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}亲爱的克莱尔\N{\rEN\blur3}Claire, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不在的时候...\N{\rEN\blur3}The rest of the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:16.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.17,0:11:17.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲\N{\rEN\blur3}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不在的时候 母亲就是我一个人的\N{\rEN\blur3}The rest of the time, Mother was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别拿走 端到这里来\N{\rEN\blur3}No, bring that here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肉里的盐分能滋养你的血液\N{\rEN\blur3}The salts in the meat will enrich your blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:40.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有胎儿的\N{\rEN\blur3}as well as the baby's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:42.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一人吃 两人补 记得吗\N{\rEN\blur3}You eat for two, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:54.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃吧\N{\rEN\blur3}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:57.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很有营养\N{\rEN\blur3}It's nutritious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:04.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守护天使\N{\rEN\blur3}Guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:06.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甜蜜的陪伴\N{\rEN\blur3}Sweet companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.17,0:12:09.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请守护我 不要离开我\N{\rEN\blur3}Stand by my side and do not leave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:14.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用你的披风庇护我 然后...\N{\rEN\blur3}Under your mantle, shelter me, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:18.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我隔着墙听到他们争论不休\N{\rEN\blur3}I would hear them through the wall, arguing incessantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:22.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对着彼此大吼大叫 话题关于财富和庄园 还有我\N{\rEN\blur3}yelling at each other about wealth, estate... and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们的争吵声让我万分恐惧\N{\rEN\blur3}Their voices filled me with fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:32.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈\N{\rEN\blur3}Maman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.04,0:12:35.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈\N{\rEN\blur3}Maman?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.75,0:12:48.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个男人鄙视我们两个\N{\rEN\blur3}The man despised us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:52.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讨厌我们乌黑的头发 深色的瞳孔\N{\rEN\blur3}Our raven black hair, our deep, dark eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.71,0:12:56.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就连我们喜好安静 不时紧张的性情\N{\rEN\blur3}Even our quiet, at times nervous disposition
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:59.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}似乎也会让他大为光火\N{\rEN\blur3}seemed to exasperate him to no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:05.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古代把体液分为哪几类\N{\rEN\blur3}List as accurately as you can the ancient classification
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽量说精确一点\N{\rEN\blur3}of the humors in the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.38,0:13:11.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}血液 黑胆汁 黄胆汁和黏液\N{\rEN\blur3}Blood, black bile, yellow bile, and phlegm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男性心脏的平均重量是多少\N{\rEN\blur3}Average male heart. Weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}250到310克 父亲\N{\rEN\blur3}Nine to eleven ounces, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.54,0:13:21.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女性心脏的平均重量\N{\rEN\blur3}Average female heart. Weight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.17,0:13:24.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}230到280克\N{\rEN\blur3}Eight to ten ounces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么觉得\N{\rEN\blur3}Why do you suppose that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:29.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女性的心脏会轻一点\N{\rEN\blur3}Difference in mass in female heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:31.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是因为她们情感更强烈\N{\rEN\blur3}Depth of emotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更容易忧郁吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Tendency to the melancholic?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:39.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为质量 血流量 肌肉灌注的不同 父亲\N{\rEN\blur3}Mass. Volume of blood, Father. Muscular irrigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.04,0:13:43.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 人体组织中没有精神物质\N{\rEN\blur3}Quite. There is no spiritual content in tissue,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.33,0:13:45.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肌肉中没有情感\N{\rEN\blur3}and no emotion in a muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 请描述一下三尖瓣的主要功能\N{\rEN\blur3}Now, describe the main function of the tricuspid valve, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:54.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在想不起来了 父亲 但我肯定能想起来\N{\rEN\blur3}I cannot recall, Father, but I'm sure I will remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:56.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我相信你\N{\rEN\blur3}Yeah, I'm sure you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:13:59.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}象牙不会流血 维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}Ivory does not bleed, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但人体会\N{\rEN\blur3}Flesh does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:04.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等你想起了某个知识要点 恐怕你的病人已经一命呜呼了\N{\rEN\blur3}By the time you remember a fact, your patient could be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:05.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}懂了吗\N{\rEN\blur3}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:13.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三尖瓣的主要功能\N{\rEN\blur3}The main function of the tricuspid valve
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是防止血液反流至腔静脉\N{\rEN\blur3}is to prevent the reflux of blood into the vena cava.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:22.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不打手了 再也不打了\N{\rEN\blur3}No, not your hands. Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:26.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它们如今是你施展技艺的工具 是你意志的延伸\N{\rEN\blur3}They are now the instruments of your craft and will,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:29.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要好好保护\N{\rEN\blur3}and we must care for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而你的脸 就微不足道了\N{\rEN\blur3}Your face, however, is vanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:46.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多 你沿用了我的名字 也必然要维护我的名声\N{\rEN\blur3}You bear my name, Victor, and with it my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我恳请你牢记这一点\N{\rEN\blur3}I pray you remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我感觉你有很好的牌\N{\rEN\blur3}I feel you have something very good, parce que...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三\N{\rEN\blur3}Three...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二\N{\rEN\blur3}Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:05.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一\N{\rEN\blur3}One...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:08.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能\N{\rEN\blur3}That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我来洗牌\N{\rEN\blur3}I'll shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲\N{\rEN\blur3}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈\N{\rEN\blur3}Maman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲 母亲出事了\N{\rEN\blur3}Father! Father. It's Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈\N{\rEN\blur3}Maman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准备好热水和干净的亚麻布 多拿一点 快\N{\rEN\blur3}I need hot water and clean linen. A lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 先生\N{\rEN\blur3}-Now. -Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-不 维克多  -母亲\N{\rEN\blur3}-No, Victor! -Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-妈妈 -维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}-Maman! -Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲\N{\rEN\blur3}Father! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定要救她 求你了\N{\rEN\blur3}-Victor! -Save her, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.92,0:16:41.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的母亲 我曾将她视作我的一部分\N{\rEN\blur3}My mother, whom I had come to consider a part of my very self,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:44.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我曾以为她永远不会离去\N{\rEN\blur3}she who I thought would never leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:49.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以为她是我的生命 如今她死了\N{\rEN\blur3}she who was life... was now death.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:52.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的双眼已暗淡无光\N{\rEN\blur3}Her eyes extinguished,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:57.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑容被冰冷的土地埋葬\N{\rEN\blur3}her smile feeding the cold earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走开\N{\rEN\blur3}Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都给我走开\N{\rEN\blur3}All of you, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:17.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的世界空了一块\N{\rEN\blur3}A part of the universe had been hollowed out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的头顶笼罩着永远的黑暗\N{\rEN\blur3}and the firmament was now permanently dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:26.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遮住眼睛\N{\rEN\blur3}Now, cover your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫你看再看哦\N{\rEN\blur3}Don't look until I tell you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:33.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看吧\N{\rEN\blur3}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:36.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}威廉在阳光和笑容中长大\N{\rEN\blur3}William grew full of sunshine and smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:41.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的性情比我平和温顺 显然更讨父亲喜欢\N{\rEN\blur3}He was of a calmer, gentler disposition, clearly favored by my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你 父亲\N{\rEN\blur3}Thank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不客气 儿子\N{\rEN\blur3}Oh, it's a pleasure, my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是宜人的微风 我是滚滚的黑云\N{\rEN\blur3}He was the breeze, I was the storm cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:53.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他带来欢声笑语 我让人愁眉不展\N{\rEN\blur3}He was all laughter, I was all frowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:55.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿起缰绳\N{\rEN\blur3}Pick up the reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.50,0:17:58.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲 看我做得怎么样\N{\rEN\blur3}Look at me, Father. Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.79,0:18:01.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不止如此\N{\rEN\blur3}There was something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:05.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更确切地说 某些东西被忽视了\N{\rEN\blur3}Or rather, something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的母亲\N{\rEN\blur3}My mother had died
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:12.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死在如日中天的名医\N{\rEN\blur3}at the hands of the most distinguished doctor of his day:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的父亲手下\N{\rEN\blur3}My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:18.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的脑中渐渐有了个想法\N{\rEN\blur3}An idea... took shape in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请说说《心血运动论》中...\N{\rEN\blur3}Define the circulatory system, if you will...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:24.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无可避免 无法逃避\N{\rEN\blur3}Inevitable, unavoidable...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:28.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}...对循环系统是怎么定义的\N{\rEN\blur3}...as enunciated in De Motu Cordis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}...直到这个想法被说了出来\N{\rEN\blur3}...until it became truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲\N{\rEN\blur3}Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没救她 对吗\N{\rEN\blur3}You let her die, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:41.12,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我用尽全力救她了 你必须知道这一点\N{\rEN\blur3}I did everything in my power to save her. You must know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说 你失败了\N{\rEN\blur3}So you failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:45.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没人能战胜死亡\N{\rEN\blur3}-No one can conquer death. -Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:52.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能 我会战胜的\N{\rEN\blur3}I will. I will conquer it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会掌握你掌握的所有知识 还会更进一步\N{\rEN\blur3}Everything you know, I will know. And more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:19:01.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天就到此为止吧\N{\rEN\blur3}I think we've done quite enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:06.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那晚我重生了\N{\rEN\blur3}I was born anew that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看到了幻象\N{\rEN\blur3}I had a vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:12.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我第一次看到了\N{\rEN\blur3}I saw, for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:14.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黑暗天使\N{\rEN\blur3}the Dark Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它向我许下承诺\N{\rEN\blur3}And it made me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:35.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我将能掌控生死\N{\rEN\blur3}I would have command over the forces of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:40.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成为和父亲一样杰出的外科医生\N{\rEN\blur3}I would become every ounce the surgeon my father was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:43.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的野心和成就将超过他\N{\rEN\blur3}I would surpass him in ambition and in reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.50,0:19:44.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守护天使...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.63,0:19:46.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幻象如此清晰\N{\rEN\blur3}The vision was so clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:51.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论清醒还是睡梦中 我都从未看到如此清晰的景象\N{\rEN\blur3}Clearer than anything I'd ever seen in my waking hours or dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:55.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但承诺如何兑现\N{\rEN\blur3}But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:21.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的境遇很快一落千丈\N{\rEN\blur3}My downfall was swift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:25.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}母亲的种植园 经历了两次叛乱和一场火灾\N{\rEN\blur3}Two revolts and a fire on my mother's plantations
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家族财富因此锐减\N{\rEN\blur3}dwindled the family fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:31.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}庄园留下了 但别的全都没了\N{\rEN\blur3}We kept the estate, but lost everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:49.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}威廉被送去了维也纳的亲戚家\N{\rEN\blur3}William went to one side of the family in Vienna
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去了伦敦 然后又去了爱丁堡\N{\rEN\blur3}and I to London, then Edinburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:56.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那里 我花了数十年时间\N{\rEN\blur3}And there, for decades, I tried to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:02.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尝试为狭隘的学术界拓宽边界\N{\rEN\blur3}expand the narrow limits of academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生命\N{\rEN\blur3}Life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:10.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}这就是生命 先生们\N{\rEN\blur3}This... is life, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}(皇家医学院纪律法庭 1855年)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们出生了\N{\rEN\blur3}We are born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:18.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚上去没多久 就掉下来了\N{\rEN\blur3}Hmm? And no sooner do we rise, we fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:20.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死了\N{\rEN\blur3}Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这一起一落之间\N{\rEN\blur3}And in the space between that rise and fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:27.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是我们渺小卑微的一生\N{\rEN\blur3}our humble little purview.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出生不为我们所控\N{\rEN\blur3}Now, birth is not in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不对\N{\rEN\blur3}Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:40.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生命之火的点燃 思想和灵魂的诞生\N{\rEN\blur3}Conception, that spark, the animation of thought and soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.21,0:21:42.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}掌握在上帝的手中\N{\rEN\blur3}That is in God's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.33,0:21:44.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上帝\N{\rEN\blur3}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:46.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而死亡\N{\rEN\blur3}But death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}挑战正在此处\N{\rEN\blur3}Ah, now there lies the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死亡应该掌握在我们手中\N{\rEN\blur3}That should be our concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该如此\N{\rEN\blur3}It should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们凭什么能掌控  我们又不是神明 对不对\N{\rEN\blur3}Who are we to do so? We are not gods, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:02.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但要是我们能像神明那般大胆\N{\rEN\blur3}But if we are to behave as immodestly as gods,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.67,0:22:05.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那至少能够创造奇迹\N{\rEN\blur3}we must, at the very least, deliver miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.13,0:22:07.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是\N{\rEN\blur3}Wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:12.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在年轻学子心中点燃神圣火花\N{\rEN\blur3}Ignite a divine spark in these young students' minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.46,0:22:15.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教导他们抛弃顺从 违抗权威\N{\rEN\blur3}Teach them defiance rather than obedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:21.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}展示人类有可能掌控自然奥秘 让死亡不再发生\N{\rEN\blur3}Show that man may pursue nature to her hiding places and stop death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.46,0:22:24.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是延缓死亡 而是长生不老\N{\rEN\blur3}Not slow it down, but stop it entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:33.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}安静\N{\rEN\blur3}Silence. Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.92,0:22:42.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种不可能的事 你究竟要怎么教\N{\rEN\blur3}How exactly do you propose to teach what is impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.71,0:22:48.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人类的尸体 一个复合实体\N{\rEN\blur3}Composite subject, the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:51.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是某个店老板 刚咽气没多久就送到了我这里\N{\rEN\blur3}That of a shopkeeper, delivered mere moments after expiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.96,0:22:53.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大脑暴露在外 但仍能运作\N{\rEN\blur3}The brain laid bare but functional,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.54,0:22:56.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脊神经分支和迷走神经完好无损\N{\rEN\blur3}the spinal branches and vagal nerves intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:59.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家或许能看到一些极细的伤口\N{\rEN\blur3}You may observe the hair-thin scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.04,0:23:01.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的手艺无需粗糙的缝合\N{\rEN\blur3}No coarse stitching needed by my own technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:03.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看这条手臂\N{\rEN\blur3}The arm, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:05.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来自某个木匠\N{\rEN\blur3}comes from another specimen, that of a carpenter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.63,0:23:08.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}肌肉 韧带 神经 都已连结好\N{\rEN\blur3}The muscles, ligaments, nerves, all connected now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:32.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看啊 电流导致躯体痉挛\N{\rEN\blur3}Now, the spasmodic movement of the body
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:34.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这已不是新鲜事\N{\rEN\blur3}caused from the electric current, this is not new.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:37.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都见过 不过 这种躯体内的能量流动\N{\rEN\blur3}It's not new. However, the flow of energy through the body
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.71,0:23:39.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遵循一种完全不同的概念\N{\rEN\blur3}follows a different notion entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一种称为气的东方概念\N{\rEN\blur3}An Eastern notion called qi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.92,0:23:45.12,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种概念认为 生命能量的流动 同时存在于身体内外\N{\rEN\blur3}Now, it considers the vital flow of energy both within and without.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.13,0:23:46.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我用针在六个...\N{\rEN\blur3}I'm utilizing needles in six--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:51.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安静 都坐下\N{\rEN\blur3}Quiet! Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:56.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}医生 这是听证会 不是狂欢节表演\N{\rEN\blur3}This is a hearing, Doctor, not a carnival act.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:58.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这样无济于事 维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}You're not helping your cause, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:24:00.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种用电的诡计根本没用\N{\rEN\blur3}This galvanic trickery will simply not do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:01.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诡计\N{\rEN\blur3}Trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:04.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诡计\N{\rEN\blur3}Trickery?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:08.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你确定吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.21,0:24:15.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不是诡计 而是一种抉择\N{\rEN\blur3}That is not trickery. That is a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:20.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个死人的眼睛 和另一个死人的胳膊协调运动\N{\rEN\blur3}Motor coordination between the eye of one dead man and the arm of another,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.17,0:24:23.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注入全新的意志和基本的理解力\N{\rEN\blur3}infused with a new will and the rudiments of understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:27.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经死亡的大脑也有理解力吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Understanding in a brain that already died?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.54,0:24:29.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放开\N{\rEN\blur3}Release now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.04,0:24:31.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请放开\N{\rEN\blur3}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.46,0:24:34.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}礼貌一点总有效果\N{\rEN\blur3}"Please" always helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.00,0:24:39.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赶紧关了吧 你个江湖骗子\N{\rEN\blur3}Turn that off at once. At once, you charlatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.17,0:24:42.12,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是未来 这是有可能实现的\N{\rEN\blur3}This is the future. This is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.13,0:24:44.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不研究一下 量化一下呢\N{\rEN\blur3}Why not study it? Why not quantify it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.29,0:24:50.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是罪恶的 可恨 下流\N{\rEN\blur3}This is unholy. An abomination. An obscenity!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.17,0:24:55.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}生命由上帝赐予 由上帝收回 维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}God gives life, and God takes it, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.92,0:24:58.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许上帝就是无能\N{\rEN\blur3}Perhaps God is inept!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.92,0:25:02.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要由我们来纠正他的错误\N{\rEN\blur3}And it is we that must amend his mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.33,0:25:04.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别让这些老蠢货阻止你自由表达\N{\rEN\blur3}Do not let these old fools extinguish your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.96,0:25:08.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有采取不盲从的态度 摆脱恐惧和恃强凌弱的教条\N{\rEN\blur3}The answers only come when coaxed by disobedience,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.42,0:25:11.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}答案才会浮现\N{\rEN\blur3}free of fear and cowardly dogma!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.88,0:25:27.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}克伦佩教授\N{\rEN\blur3}Professor Krempe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.04,0:26:05.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弗兰肯斯坦男爵 我叫海因里希·哈兰德\N{\rEN\blur3}Baron Frankenstein, my name is Heinrich Harlander,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.88,0:26:08.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我这里有一封\N{\rEN\blur3}and I carry with me a letter of introduction
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.71,0:26:10.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的弟弟威廉写的介绍信\N{\rEN\blur3}from your brother, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.17,0:26:11.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我弟弟\N{\rEN\blur3}From my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.21,0:26:13.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望能有幸认识你\N{\rEN\blur3}I asked for the privilege of your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.67,0:26:15.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}耽误你一点时间\N{\rEN\blur3}It won't take but a minute of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.63,0:26:16.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-请进 -好\N{\rEN\blur3}-Please. -Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.58,0:26:21.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说 威廉要来看我 对吗\N{\rEN\blur3}So William is coming to see me, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.46,0:26:24.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对 几天后到\N{\rEN\blur3}Yeah, in a matter of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:29.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他想让你见见他的未婚妻 也就是我的侄女\N{\rEN\blur3}He wants to introduce you to his fiancée. My niece, as it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.42,0:26:36.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她叫伊丽莎白·哈兰德 是一位非常可爱的小姐\N{\rEN\blur3}Elizabeth Harlander, a very nice young lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.21,0:26:37.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚刚从修道院学校毕业\N{\rEN\blur3}fresh from convent life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.42,0:26:39.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些照片都是我拍的\N{\rEN\blur3}The photographs are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.92,0:26:43.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}威廉在金融领域很有成就\N{\rEN\blur3}William has become quite successful in the world of finance.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.04,0:26:44.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}弗兰肯斯坦的名声越来越响了\N{\rEN\blur3}He's making a name for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.83,0:26:47.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎哟 是吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Ha! A name? For himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.50,0:26:52.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要知道我们都是弗兰肯斯坦 不管我们乐不乐意\N{\rEN\blur3}Well, I'm afraid we both share that name, whether we like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.13,0:26:54.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我拜读了你在《柳叶刀》上的文章\N{\rEN\blur3}I read your article in The Lancet.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.38,0:26:57.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的觉得这事能做到吗\N{\rEN\blur3}You really believe you can do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.29,0:26:59.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}组装出一个人来\N{\rEN\blur3}Assemble a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.58,0:27:03.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做出完整的全新人体 还要有生命\N{\rEN\blur3}A full new body? And give it life?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.79,0:27:06.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你今天也看到了\N{\rEN\blur3}You saw it today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.21,0:27:08.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说真的 我看到的是你当众受难\N{\rEN\blur3}What I saw was a crucifixion, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.63,0:27:11.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还没开口说句话 就被钉死了\N{\rEN\blur3}You were done for before you uttered a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.33,0:27:12.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我还是向他们展示了\N{\rEN\blur3}I still showed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.88,0:27:14.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}展示什么\N{\rEN\blur3}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.71,0:27:15.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事实\N{\rEN\blur3}The truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.42,0:27:18.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们到晚餐时间就忘了\N{\rEN\blur3}They will forget by suppertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.50,0:27:21.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话虽如此 你觉得怎么样\N{\rEN\blur3}Yes, yes, yes. But what did you think? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.04,0:27:25.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得非常厉害\N{\rEN\blur3}I thought it was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.08,0:27:28.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错 我就知道\N{\rEN\blur3}It was. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.17,0:27:31.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但你有点孩子气 太激动了\N{\rEN\blur3}But you are like a child, so excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.04,0:27:34.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紧抓你的新宠物 快把它勒死了\N{\rEN\blur3}clutching your new pet so tightly that you're strangling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.50,0:27:37.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不免为你担心\N{\rEN\blur3}That is why I worry about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.71,0:27:41.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能控制好火种吗 普罗米修斯\N{\rEN\blur3}Can you contain your fire, Prometheus?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.17,0:27:44.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是没等把它交出去 就先烧伤了自己的手\N{\rEN\blur3}Or are you going to burn your hands before delivering it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.54,0:27:47.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说得对\N{\rEN\blur3}Quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.42,0:27:51.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请不要觉得我无礼 但这一天已经足够漫长\N{\rEN\blur3}Please do not think me rude, but my day has proven long enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.92,0:27:55.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的状态也完全不适合 再陪伴陌生人了\N{\rEN\blur3}and I believe myself totally unfit for the company of strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.04,0:27:56.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果没有什么别的事了...\N{\rEN\blur3}So if there's nothing more--
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.63,0:27:58.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有重要的事\N{\rEN\blur3}Oh, but there is. Much more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.21,0:28:03.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在爱丁堡找好了住处\N{\rEN\blur3}I've taken quarters in Edinburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.67,0:28:07.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}三天后 我们一起见威廉和伊丽莎白\N{\rEN\blur3}Three days from now, we are to meet with William and Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.17,0:28:10.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我将在那晚改变你的命运\N{\rEN\blur3}And that evening, I will change your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.71,0:28:14.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会让你看到非同凡响的东西\N{\rEN\blur3}I will show you something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.08,0:28:24.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-你真好 -谢谢 给
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.42,0:28:35.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}桃子 把桃子转过来\N{\rEN\blur3}The peach. The peach. Turn the peach. Turn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.71,0:28:38.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你又啃了\N{\rEN\blur3}You bit it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.33,0:28:40.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一直在吃桃\N{\rEN\blur3}You're eating the peaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.50,0:28:43.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是对死亡的沉思\N{\rEN\blur3}This is a memento mori.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.04,0:28:49.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}桃子是生命和青春的符号 怎么就被你啃了\N{\rEN\blur3}The peach, symbol of life and youth, and you bite into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.42,0:28:51.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-我饿了呀 小希 -别那样叫我\N{\rEN\blur3}-I was hungry, Kiki. -Don't call me Kiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.71,0:28:53.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 维克多·弗兰肯斯坦男爵来了\N{\rEN\blur3}Baron Victor Frankenstein, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.04,0:28:56.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可以下去了\N{\rEN\blur3}You can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.67,0:28:58.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉\N{\rEN\blur3}Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.33,0:29:01.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎\N{\rEN\blur3}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.21,0:29:02.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈兰德先生\N{\rEN\blur3}Herr Harlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.21,0:29:05.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是一种新兴艺术 摄影\N{\rEN\blur3}A young art, photography.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.88,0:29:07.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见 小希\N{\rEN\blur3}Goodbye, Kiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.33,0:29:09.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经迷上了\N{\rEN\blur3}Already a passion of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.75,0:29:11.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}文件都带来了吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Did you bring the papers?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.54,0:29:13.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢\N{\rEN\blur3}Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.21,0:29:19.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-你非常出色 -谢谢\N{\rEN\blur3}-You're extraordinary. -Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.38,0:29:27.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你利用神经系统来传递能量脉冲\N{\rEN\blur3}You're using the nervous system to deliver the surge of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.71,0:29:29.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.67,0:29:30.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错\N{\rEN\blur3}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.92,0:29:35.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因此 你所操控的生命力 只能维持很短时间\N{\rEN\blur3}And thus the sustainability of the life force you command
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.00,0:29:38.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很快就会衰退 消散\N{\rEN\blur3}is very brief, wanes, evaporates.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.00,0:29:41.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么这么说\N{\rEN\blur3}How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.00,0:29:48.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当时你颇为自豪地结束了演示\N{\rEN\blur3}At the lecture, you ended your demonstration out of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.42,0:29:53.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但其实是因为 那股电流般的生命力\N{\rEN\blur3}But really, because the galvanic life force
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.67,0:29:55.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经衰竭了 对吗\N{\rEN\blur3}was already fading, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.50,0:29:57.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 你是外科医生吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Are you yourself a surgeon, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.71,0:30:00.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曾经是 我是战地医生\N{\rEN\blur3}Yeah, once upon a time. An army surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.04,0:30:02.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}医术也说不上多精湛\N{\rEN\blur3}Not a particularly skilled one, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.71,0:30:05.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但也给我打下了发家致富的基础\N{\rEN\blur3}But it allowed me to secure the rudiments of my fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.96,0:30:07.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在有几家军火工厂\N{\rEN\blur3}I own a few ammunition factories.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.96,0:30:10.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-你是军火商 -不如说是个务实的\N{\rEN\blur3}-An arms merchant. -A realist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.46,0:30:13.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你对伊夫林解剖图表熟悉吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Are you familiar with the Evelyn Tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.33,0:30:15.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当然 那是约翰·伊夫林爵士当年\N{\rEN\blur3}Of course. Acquired by Sir John Evelyn,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.96,0:30:18.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}买下的四张人体标本精细解剖图\N{\rEN\blur3}there are four planks, meticulous dissection,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.00,0:30:20.12,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是欧洲最早的人体神经 和动静脉解剖图\N{\rEN\blur3}some of the oldest in Europe, presenting the nerves,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.13,0:30:22.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么会提到这个\N{\rEN\blur3}veins and arteries of cadavers. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.08,0:30:24.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为还有第五张\N{\rEN\blur3}Yes. But there's a fifth one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.92,0:30:26.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这张最让人信服\N{\rEN\blur3}The most compelling one.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.33,0:30:33.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常细致 是不是\N{\rEN\blur3}Exquisite, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.50,0:30:36.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呈现于木头上的鲜活血肉\N{\rEN\blur3}Flesh rendered onto wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.29,0:30:41.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尸体放在木板上 逐层剥离\N{\rEN\blur3}The cadaver lies on the plank, is peeled away layer by layer,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.58,0:30:45.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用树脂将剩下的组织固定在木板上\N{\rEN\blur3}and the remaining tissue is lacquered with resin onto the wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.38,0:30:48.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-这是淋巴系统 -没错\N{\rEN\blur3}-It showcases the lymphatic system. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.75,0:30:52.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穆斯林医学家称其为隐秘的循环系统\N{\rEN\blur3}Muslim medics called it the secret circulatory system.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.63,0:30:58.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仅仅输送三升体液 却构成了庞大的网络\N{\rEN\blur3}It moves a mere three liters of fluid, but it's a vast network.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.21,0:31:00.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-真是非同凡响 -确实\N{\rEN\blur3}-Oh, it's remarkable. -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.17,0:31:05.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在对我们 也是对你而言 关键的改变就在这里\N{\rEN\blur3}Now for us, for you, the important variation is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.63,0:31:10.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这第九种构造 环绕心脏的结构\N{\rEN\blur3}The ninth configuration. A very delicate,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.29,0:31:13.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}极为精巧 近乎空灵\N{\rEN\blur3}almost ethereal structure surrounding the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.75,0:31:17.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既能分配能量 也能储存能量\N{\rEN\blur3}It can distribute, but also store energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.79,0:31:23.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你能在不破坏周围组织的前提下\N{\rEN\blur3}Yes, if you can access that without destroying
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.25,0:31:25.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-触达这一构造... -不 不是前面\N{\rEN\blur3}-the surrounding tissue---No. Not through the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.88,0:31:29.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是后面 脊柱 胸曲\N{\rEN\blur3}The back, spinal column, thoracic curvature.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.96,0:31:30.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没错\N{\rEN\blur3}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.83,0:31:36.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}远超人们想象的能量流动 瘢痕形成和组织再生\N{\rEN\blur3}Flow of energy, scarring and regeneration beyond anyone's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.33,0:31:37.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永生\N{\rEN\blur3}Life eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.71,0:31:43.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我将提供无限的资源 来支持你的研究\N{\rEN\blur3}I will endow your pursuit with unlimited resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.79,0:31:47.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我要拿什么来交换\N{\rEN\blur3}And in exchange?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.75,0:31:50.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说就俗了\N{\rEN\blur3}No need to become indelicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.25,0:31:54.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们探寻真理 志在超越 有着共同的追求\N{\rEN\blur3}We're searchers for truth and transcendence, kindred spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.42,0:31:58.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}某天我也许会请你帮个忙 作为回报\N{\rEN\blur3}I may in time ask you for a favor in return,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.38,0:32:02.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但最重要的是记录研究过程 以传诸后世的这份特权\N{\rEN\blur3}but it's mostly the privilege to record your process for posterity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.46,0:32:03.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我习惯独自工作\N{\rEN\blur3}I work alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:06.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我绝对不出声\N{\rEN\blur3}I'm very quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.17,0:32:09.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈兰德先生 威廉·弗兰肯斯坦和您的侄女到了\N{\rEN\blur3}William Frankenstein and your niece, Herr Harlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.08,0:32:14.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要考虑一下\N{\rEN\blur3}I shall consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.54,0:32:16.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会考虑的\N{\rEN\blur3}I'll consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.96,0:32:18.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男爵\N{\rEN\blur3}Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.13,0:32:23.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别假装冷静了 错过了就可惜了\N{\rEN\blur3}Don't pretend to be reasonable now. It would be such a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.63,0:32:34.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.96,0:32:36.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}威廉\N{\rEN\blur3}William!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.17,0:32:38.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-维克多 -瞧瞧你\N{\rEN\blur3}-Victor. -Look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.96,0:32:41.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老天 你长大了\N{\rEN\blur3}My, you've grown.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.63,0:32:43.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惜不是我的功劳\N{\rEN\blur3}Through no merit of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.04,0:32:46.04,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来见见我的未婚妻吧\N{\rEN\blur3}May I introduce the woman I'm to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.71,0:32:48.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊丽莎白·哈兰德小姐\N{\rEN\blur3}Lady Elizabeth Harlander.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.71,0:33:11.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}荣幸之至\N{\rEN\blur3}Absolutely delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.96,0:33:19.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听到你被驱逐 说实话我也不惊讶\N{\rEN\blur3}Can't say I was shocked when you were expelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.88,0:33:22.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他们的态度太强硬 言语太狠毒\N{\rEN\blur3}but the manner and virulence of your expulsion,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.46,0:33:23.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认为实在没有必要\N{\rEN\blur3}uncalled for, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.71,0:33:24.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有必要\N{\rEN\blur3}No, it was called for. I earned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.92,0:33:26.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我应得的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.50,0:33:29.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我特意挣来的 你说是不是 哈兰德先生\N{\rEN\blur3}I made it a point to earn it, wouldn't you say, Herr Harlander?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.00,0:33:30.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}确实声势浩大\N{\rEN\blur3}It was quite an exit, I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.33,0:33:33.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要激怒他们\N{\rEN\blur3}Why provoke them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.42,0:33:37.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何不继续做自己的事 避免惹来不必要的关注\N{\rEN\blur3}Why not just carry on without calling attention to yourself in such a manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.96,0:33:41.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}威廉 就算以你的标准来看 这么做也太保守了\N{\rEN\blur3}How safe, even by your standards, William.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.71,0:33:43.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这话听着都有点像父亲了\N{\rEN\blur3}You almost sound like Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.67,0:33:47.12,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父亲可是相当老练的\N{\rEN\blur3}He was a most tactful man, our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.13,0:33:50.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他做事精准 谨慎 有分寸感\N{\rEN\blur3}He was precise, discreet, measured.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.83,0:33:55.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就不是 我完全不懂为何谦虚是一种美德\N{\rEN\blur3}I, on the other hand, fail to see why modesty is considered a virtue at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.38,0:33:57.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}维克多一直这么引人注目\N{\rEN\blur3}Victor's always been one to harvest attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.33,0:34:01.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即便在小时候 我也常常 通过保持沉默 来消解他的声音\N{\rEN\blur3}Even as children, I mitigated his voice by staying silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.63,0:34:04.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的事发生无数次了吧 维克多 你说呢\N{\rEN\blur3}Perhaps too much and far too many times, wouldn't you say, Victor?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.58,0:34:06.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果可以再造生命\N{\rEN\blur3}If life can be regenerated,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.96,0:34:08.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并非简单的模拟\N{\rEN\blur3}not as a mere simulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.21,0:34:13.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是通过物理化学手段 如神迹般地再造 何不大声说出来\N{\rEN\blur3}but as a divine act by physical, chemical means, why whisper it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.00,0:34:16.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你笑了\N{\rEN\blur3}You laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.38,0:34:19.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-你觉得好笑吗  -没错\N{\rEN\blur3}-You're amused? -I must be, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.71,0:34:21.12,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的理念没表达清楚吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Are my ideas not clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.13,0:34:23.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你显然已经够大声的了\N{\rEN\blur3}You certainly expressed them loudly enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.67,0:34:25.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不值得为之努力吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Are they not worthwhile?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.00,0:34:27.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我认为理念本身并不值得为之努力\N{\rEN\blur3}Ideas are not worthwhile by themselves, I don't believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.25,0:34:31.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愿闻其详\N{\rEN\blur3}Enlighten me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.17,0:34:34.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿战争来说\N{\rEN\blur3}Take the war, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.38,0:34:37.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}威廉 去书房享用雪茄和白兰地吧\N{\rEN\blur3}William, cigar and brandy in my study?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.58,0:34:41.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我侄女的长篇大论你肯定都听过了\N{\rEN\blur3}Surely you've heard my niece expound on the matter before.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.42,0:34:43.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们失陪了\N{\rEN\blur3}You'll excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.29,0:34:50.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请继续说 关于理念\N{\rEN\blur3}Pray, carry on. Ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.46,0:34:57.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么说吧 荣耀 国家 勇气\N{\rEN\blur3}Well... honor, country, valor.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.63,0:35:01.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些必然是值得为之奋斗的崇高理念\N{\rEN\blur3}These surely are worthwhile, elevated ideas by themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.71,0:35:02.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同意吧\N{\rEN\blur3}wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.29,0:35:06.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而 人们为了这些理念赴死\N{\rEN\blur3}-Mm-hmm. -And nevertheless, men are dying for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.04,0:35:08.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以一种显然毫不崇高的方式\N{\rEN\blur3}In a decidedly un-elevated way,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.96,0:35:11.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}脸埋在泥泞里 喉咙呛着血\N{\rEN\blur3}face down in the mud, choking on blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.92,0:35:13.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛得大喊大叫\N{\rEN\blur3}screaming in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.04,0:35:17.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们是某人的父亲 兄弟或儿子\N{\rEN\blur3}Men that were fathers, brothers or sons to someone out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.38,0:35:19.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们被自己的母亲带到这个世界\N{\rEN\blur3}Men that were fed, cleaned and nursed
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.38,0:35:21.33,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被悉心喂养 洗净 照料 教育\N{\rEN\blur3}and schooled into this world by their mothers,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.92,0:35:23.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后却被送到某个遥远的战场\N{\rEN\blur3}only to fall on a battlefield far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.88,0:35:26.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真正制造惨剧的人却躲得远远的\N{\rEN\blur3}far from those that provoke these tragedies.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.38,0:35:31.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们好好地待在家中 不沾血 不挨刀\N{\rEN\blur3}Those men remain at home, untouched by blood or bayonet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.42,0:35:35.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}皮肤完好无损 被窝温暖洁净\N{\rEN\blur3}their skin unpierced, their blankets warm and clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.13,0:35:40.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是蠢人追求理念的后果\N{\rEN\blur3}That is what happens when ideas are pursued by fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.88,0:35:42.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你觉得我是蠢人\N{\rEN\blur3}And you think me a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.33,0:35:47.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快享用你的白兰地和雪茄去吧\N{\rEN\blur3}Run to your brandy and cigars.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.58,0:35:49.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们都在等着呢\N{\rEN\blur3}The boys are waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.33,0:36:01.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人常常以为遇见了天使或魔鬼\N{\rEN\blur3}How often a man believes he's met an angel or a devil,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.67,0:36:04.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到头来却发现一切不过是幻觉\N{\rEN\blur3}only to find it is all an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.96,0:36:09.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们下的这盘棋\N{\rEN\blur3}The game of chess we play...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.92,0:36:12.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对手只有自己\N{\rEN\blur3}we play only against ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.17,0:36:16.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}帮帮他\N{\rEN\blur3}Help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.63,0:36:17.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快点\N{\rEN\blur3}Help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.67,0:36:20.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}给 喝点吧\N{\rEN\blur3}Here you go. Drink some.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.21,0:36:44.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快跟我来\N{\rEN\blur3}You better come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.88,0:36:47.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么都没有\N{\rEN\blur3}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.21,0:36:48.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生 看守人看到他了\N{\rEN\blur3}Sir, the watchman saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.79,0:36:51.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在迷雾中绕着船转\N{\rEN\blur3}Circling the ship. In the mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.46,0:36:53.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们都亲眼看他沉下去了\N{\rEN\blur3}We all saw him drown.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.17,0:36:54.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先生\N{\rEN\blur3}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.42,0:36:56.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家都很恐慌\N{\rEN\blur3}The men are terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.00,0:36:58.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觉得该把那个男人扔到冰面上\N{\rEN\blur3}They think that man should be surrendered to the ice
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.46,0:36:59.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结束这一切\N{\rEN\blur3}and be done with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.33,0:37:04.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他受我保护...\N{\rEN\blur3}He is under my protection...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.46,0:37:08.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}受王国庇佑\N{\rEN\blur3}and the protection of the Crown!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.83,0:37:24.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几周后 我 威廉和哈兰德 骑马穿过海峡\N{\rEN\blur3}A few weeks later, I rode with William and Harlander
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.79,0:37:27.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来到瓦杜兹附近的一个湖边\N{\rEN\blur3}to a lake near Vaduz across the channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.46,0:37:30.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这座塔楼是用来过滤农田灌溉用水的\N{\rEN\blur3}The tower was built as a water filtration plant to irrigate the fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.96,0:37:33.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是个公共工程项目 所以战争一开始就被弃建了\N{\rEN\blur3}Public works, so construction was abandoned at the start of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.08,0:37:36.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是这场战争 是前一场\N{\rEN\blur3}Not this war, the one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.54,0:37:39.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者是再前面一场 我记不清了\N{\rEN\blur3}Or the one before that, I cannot quite remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.50,0:37:46.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一看到它\N{\rEN\blur3}The moment I laid eyes on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.63,0:37:48.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这座塔楼\N{\rEN\blur3}The tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.38,0:37:52.88,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我便感受到了命运的召唤\N{\rEN\blur3}I could feel destiny calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.79,0:38:05.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}建筑结构基本完整\N{\rEN\blur3}The structure's basically intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.58,0:38:08.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里还有一条陡坡道 从顶上直通到底部\N{\rEN\blur3}And there's a chute going from top, right to the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.42,0:38:11.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会安排人把你的个人物品\N{\rEN\blur3}I can arrange for your belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.21,0:38:13.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从爱丁堡运过来\N{\rEN\blur3}We'll bring them from Edinburgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.96,0:38:29.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你需要什么 都能满足\N{\rEN\blur3}Anything you need or want shall be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.54,0:38:32.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-什么都可以  -什么都可以\N{\rEN\blur3}-Anything? -Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.83,0:38:45.37,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}整个项目期间 威廉随叫随到\N{\rEN\blur3}I have secured William's service for the duration of the project.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.38,0:38:46.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要一个临时密室\N{\rEN\blur3}I'll need a holding cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.58,0:38:49.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-实验室旁边要有个冷库 -威廉\N{\rEN\blur3}-And an ice chamber close to the lab. -William.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.42,0:38:52.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}塔楼底部有两个泵水库\N{\rEN\blur3}There are two pump reservoirs at the base of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.79,0:38:54.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要改造一下\N{\rEN\blur3}We'll repurpose those.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.29,0:38:56.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要重启蒸汽机\N{\rEN\blur3}We shall need to recondition the steam engines.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.29,0:38:58.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}需要足够的燃料 来保证机器正常运转\N{\rEN\blur3}We'll need enough fuel to make sure they run.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.75,0:39:02.42,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那里 还有那里 放四块高容量的伏打电池\N{\rEN\blur3}There and there, four high-capacity voltaic batteries,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.42,0:39:04.17,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正负电极\N{\rEN\blur3}positive and negative polarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.17,0:39:08.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还要一套纯银避雷针系统 向下延伸至实验室\N{\rEN\blur3}and a lightning rod system of pure silver telescoping down into the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.46,0:39:13.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没问题 你需要什么设备 我的承包商都能造出来\N{\rEN\blur3}Yes. My contractors can manufacture any and all equipment you may require.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.50,0:39:18.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 我们应该达成共识了吧\N{\rEN\blur3}I take it then that we have an understanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.21,0:39:26.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交易达成\N{\rEN\blur3}A bargain has been struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.38,0:39:38.38,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}混蛋\N{\rEN\blur3}Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.08,0:39:41.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个不行\N{\rEN\blur3}No. No. Not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.33,0:39:46.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}张嘴\N{\rEN\blur3}Aah. Open your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.42,0:39:51.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被绞死算你走运 你本就活不过今年了\N{\rEN\blur3}You, you're lucky to be hanged. You would have died within the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.54,0:39:54.12,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈兰德先生答应我 让我拿到最好的样本\N{\rEN\blur3}Herr Harlander promised me access to optimal specimens.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.13,0:39:55.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阁下 他倒是答应了\N{\rEN\blur3}Yeah, that he may have, your lordship,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.88,0:39:57.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可您也知道\N{\rEN\blur3}but as you well know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.38,0:40:00.87,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}犯罪又不是什么好差事 我们这里也只有些歪瓜裂枣\N{\rEN\blur3}crime doesn't pay, and it's a poor showing of it we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.88,0:40:02.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪个都是可怜虫\N{\rEN\blur3}They're wretches every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.71,0:40:03.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是抱歉\N{\rEN\blur3}I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.50,0:40:06.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}背很强壮 这个可以\N{\rEN\blur3}That's a strong back. This one will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.25,0:40:43.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍后再来\N{\rEN\blur3}Come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.29,0:40:44.46,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来告解\N{\rEN\blur3}Confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.13,0:40:48.21,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很好奇\N{\rEN\blur3}I was intrigued.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.46,0:40:54.75,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此纤弱又虔诚的人 能有什么要告解的\N{\rEN\blur3}What would such a delicate, pious creature have to confess to?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.13,0:41:00.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是碰巧 被我找到了一个机会\N{\rEN\blur3}As luck would have it, an opportunity presented itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.54,0:41:01.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我...\N{\rEN\blur3}and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.96,0:41:05.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就要揭开谜底了\N{\rEN\blur3}I was about to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.88,0:41:28.71,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}神父 请为我祝福 我有罪\N{\rEN\blur3}Bless me, Father, for I have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.58,0:41:33.25,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩子 你多久没告解了\N{\rEN\blur3}How long has it been since your last confession, my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.25,0:41:35.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还没到一周 神父 我在修道院待过\N{\rEN\blur3}Barely a week, Father. I was in a convent.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.04,0:41:37.13,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就一周\N{\rEN\blur3}A week?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.46,0:41:40.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就这么轻率地犯错了\N{\rEN\blur3}Tsk-tsk. Have you so hastily committed sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.58,0:41:41.58,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的\N{\rEN\blur3}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.08,0:41:43.92,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是罪孽的念头 并非实际行动\N{\rEN\blur3}Sin of intent, not deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.63,0:41:46.62,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-因为一名男子 对不对  -对\N{\rEN\blur3}-A man, is it? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.63,0:41:47.96,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我未婚夫的兄长\N{\rEN\blur3}My fiancé's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.50,0:41:50.67,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是欲念吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Lust?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.67,0:41:52.50,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-是憎恶 -憎恶...\N{\rEN\blur3}-Hatred. -Hatred...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.46,0:41:56.63,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}-憎恶  -那名男子很恶劣 很丑陋\N{\rEN\blur3}-Hatred? -The man is appalling, grotesque.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.79,0:41:59.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话很是刺耳\N{\rEN\blur3}Harsh words.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.29,0:42:01.00,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}近乎无情了 对吗\N{\rEN\blur3}Rather uncharitable, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.00,0:42:03.54,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尊敬的神父 您并不了解这个人\N{\rEN\blur3}Respectfully, Father, you do not know this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.54,0:42:07.08,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他试图操控周围一切的人和事\N{\rEN\blur3}He tries to control and manipulate everything and everyone around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.08,0:42:09.79,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他和所有暴君一样 以假扮受害者为乐\N{\rEN\blur3}Like every tyrant, he delights in playing the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.79,0:42:11.29,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要我说 那是他唯一的本事\N{\rEN\blur3}His only advantage, I would say,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.29,0:42:13.83,CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他自以为绅士 实则粗鄙不堪\N{\rEN\blur3}is he's far cruder than he believes himself to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.88,0:42:15.88,CN
